entries.femaleVariant: He better keep this short and sweet.
Hi, umm... Think something might've gone wrong here…
I'm not a customer.
Need to get in touch with Evelyn Parker. It's important.
You and me both. Tried calling her a bunch of times... No luck.
She had an accident. Needed to go to a special clinic in Osaka... or Oslo? I think it was Oslo – for a new faceplate.
Relax, ya don't need any data, don't need any detes. I'm not a customer.
She tell you she was leaving?
Osaka or Oslo – which is it?
I'm familiar with the accident.
Tell you herself she was skippin' town?
Nah, just didn't show up for work. Wasn't picking up, either, so I asked Woodman what was up.
Told me she left. Like I said.
Osaka or Oslo – which was it?
entries.maleVariant: Which was it – Osaka or Oslo?

entries.femaleVariant: Oslo... Yeah, definitely Oslo.
That accident. Involved a client, did it?
Found blood in her booth.
Could it be Woodman finally sheds some light on this shitshow? Man can only dream…
Not really sure, umm... Don't have your details. Sorry, no idea what I'm supposed to do...
Sure your VIP card checks out? Had a sich once – payment bounced and I was ripped outta the sesh the same way.
Here to talk, to you specifically. Not to be with a doll.
Tom. Is that it?
Uh-huh.
Uhh... You know, shit like that happens here... sometimes.
And everyone's cool with that?
We get new implants, recovery leave and... well, sometimes even a payout.
Where can I find this Woodman?
Who is this Woodman?
Woodman – who is he?
Where can I find this Woodman?
Probably got his feet up in the back office.
'Cept it's off limits to customers.
That'll do. Thanks.
Mr. Forrest. But everybody calls him Woodman. Never really known why…
OK, Mr. Forrest then. What's his thing?
He's kinda like our caretaker. Finds new talent, deals with ugly situations…
The skull sponges in these dolls... THAT's what they should be replacin'...
Wh-what do you want?
Relax, you're not in trouble.
Relax, not gonna hurt you.
Shut up.
Shut up and pull yourself together.
Where's Evelyn Parker?
Woodman?
Vanished where?
Vanished? Into thin air?
Looking for Evelyn Parker.
Woodman – who's he?
I don't know anything, I swear!
Just wanna talk for a little.
Y-you've got me confused with someone else! Never seen you in my life! Couldn't've done anything to you!
Evelyn? No idea what she's been up to…
Mr. Forrest. But... we all call him Woodman. Never really known why…
She went to... Think it was Oslo.
Two brainwashed sex zombies in a single day is too much, even for me.
Docked it from my pay, they did...
D-don't shoot me, don't hurt me. I didn't do anything…
Need to ask you a question, so shut up and listen.
Not fucking around, drop the act, I know you're friends. Tell me where she is.
Woodman told me she up and vanished.
Called her more than once. No answer.
Where'll I find him?
Back-office. He almost never leaves.
Where's Evelyn? Need to talk to her urgently, it's important.
She's not here. Tried callin' her more than once – no answer.
Heard she was chippin' a new faceplate at a clinic in... Osaka? No no, Oslo – that was it.
Tell you herself she was goin' away?
Osaka or Oslo – which is it?
Where can I find this Woodman?
Who is Woodman?
You mad at her or something?
No. Know where she is or not?
Osaka or Oslo – which is it?
Oslo... Yeah, definitely Oslo.
Evelyn tell you personally she was goin' away?
Nah, just didn't show up for work. Wasn't picking up neither, so I asked Woodman what was up.
Told me she left. Like I said.
Woodman – who is he?
Mr. Forrest. But we all call him Woodman. Never really known why…
OK – Mr. Forrest,  then. Who is he?
entries.maleVariant: OK, Mr. Forrest then. Who is he?

Now that I think about it, it is weird she went away so far.
You and Evelyn friends?
Heard you and Evelyn get along famously. That true?
Yeah, we go way back – always stuck together.
Why do you ask?
Woodman – that the guy who takes care of the dolls?
Why're you askin' if you already know?
Woodman – that the Forrest guy who takes care of the dolls?
Why're you askin' if you already know?
I wanna talk to Evelyn.
